  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf; \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A bear that threatens people; Many were seriously injured",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the Mannar district, Vatuppithan Madu, Nanatan, Bengali, etc., have seen an increase in bear activity, and many people have been bitten by bears. One of them has been hospitalized with serious injuries.",
        "The wildlife department is unable to catch the bear due to fuel problem.",
        "Victims report that the bear enters residential areas at night and attacks people in the early hours of the morning.",
        "A bear attacked a fisherman who was fishing last Monday night, and the concerned person has been admitted to Mannar Hospital.",
        "Therefore, the public has requested to take action to provide fuel for the wildlife department and take measures to catch the bear.",
        "The movement of the bear in the said area has been recorded on the CCTV camera in the area. (R)"
      ],
